Dan-T-1987 wrote a review Mar 8
Lutterworth, United Kingdom37 contributions
Looks can be deceiving!!
Stayed here after looking at all the amazing pictures online, and a good amount of positive reviews. Retrospectively looked at the pictures again, and realised these are almost all beachfront villas….so unless this is what room you are booking, tread carefully, as the room I was given was nothing like any of the pictures. The beach side pool was probably the best thing about the hotel…the food was terrible, the main building room I stayed in was not 5* at all. The rooms were very basic, and for some reason contained a fake kitchen with no actual kitchen amenities. The bathroom was dark and based on not being able to put toilet paper down the toilet (which is fine of course if you are aware), I’m guessing the water filtration would not suit teeth brushing. Overall, I would not…
