Most satisfied accommodation!!
Our manager 'Jasmine' was kind, and the feedback was quick. The room was clean and the room temperature is pleasant. Everything the manager asked for was perfect! We use apartment. The all facilities and environment were good. The breakfast menu changed every day and was delicious, and the vegetables and fruits were fresh. We were very satisfied with the accommodation!
