Jane L wrote a review Feb 2024
Singapore17 contributions
Pool villa with 3 bedrooms
It is an idyllic beachfront location halfway between Danang and Hoi An, best of both worlds. Also right next door to two golf courses. The villa is luxurious and self containing with free standing bathtubs in two of the rooms. It is one of the best timeshare holiday facility I have stayed in.
