Feel like in paradise
A dream location. You feel like in paradise. The beach is superb and you are not disturbed by anything. The rooms are very large and clean. The experience in the villa is very beautiful. The staff are very friendly and willing to solve any request at any time. Only words of praise for Min, the person who took care of our stay.
