Great hotel by the beach with exceptional service
I had a fantastic experience at Nama Retreat; Min, our host, offered outstanding assistance and recommendations throughout our stay in Da Nang. The breakfast options were excellent, catering to all preferences. Thanks to Min, securing daily massages was a breeze as she consistently booked them for us. Highly recommend for an enjoyable and stress-free stay!
