Frequently Asked Questions about Naman Retreat
Which popular attractions are close to Naman Retreat?
Nearby attractions include Non Nuoc Beach (3.0 miles), The Marble Mountains (2.7 miles), and Hoa Nghiem Cave (2.6 miles).
See all nearby attractions.
What are some of the property amenities at Naman Retreat?
Some of the more popular amenities offered include free wifi, free breakfast, and a pool.
See all property amenities.
Which room amenities are available at Naman Retreat?
Top room amenities include a minibar, air conditioning, and a flat screen TV.
See all room amenities.
What food & drink options are available at Naman Retreat?
Guests can enjoy free breakfast, an on-site restaurant, and a lounge during their stay.
Learn more.
Is parking available at Naman Retreat?
Yes, free parking, a parking garage, and secured parking are available to guests.
What are some restaurants close to Naman Retreat?
Conveniently located restaurants include Table 88, La Plage, and The Grill Restaurant.
See all nearby restaurants.
Are there opportunities to exercise at Naman Retreat?
Yes, guests have access to a pool, a fitness center, and a sauna during their stay.
Does Naman Retreat have airport transportation?
Yes, Naman Retreat offers airport transportation for guests. We recommend calling ahead to confirm details.
Are any cleaning services offered at Naman Retreat?
Yes, dry cleaning and laundry service are offered to guests.
Does Naman Retreat offer any business services?
Yes, it conveniently offers a business center, meeting rooms, and a banquet room.
Which languages are spoken by the staff at Naman Retreat?
The staff speaks multiple languages, including English, Chinese, Japanese, Vietnamese, and Korean.
